<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TW7J3pG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Edit: This is a real Dunning Kruger effect and I don't mean that as an insult. A lot of people have never thought about how big a hospital is and how clean it has to be. Think if a pt vomits on the wall and its green will anyone even notice? imagine what could be passed on in that time. if there are fake plants they collect dust, insects, etc, and they need to be thoroughly cleaned. Floors are white so you can see bodily fluids more easily. Imagine someone urinating on the floor, but because of the color its hard to tell if its water or urine when cleaning. after cleaning 400 rooms that day maybe the Janitor thinks they hit that spot already and leaves it. Its a huge knowledge gap that people don't always think about but staggeringly important.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ETFQVmV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[softspokensatan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Staring? Me? Never!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zjFSE3y</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rDBsQHR.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.youtube.com/crackermilk</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zjFSE3y</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Buenos días, mundo.... (SONIDO)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/c1S91ki</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G5Jg687.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Google Translator.- Good morning, world.... (SOUND)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/c1S91ki</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[exploradoresciclos2018]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Who wants to bathe with this beauty?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AXTC22J</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://